condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 1. (a) | Description :Maintain throughout period of Project Implementation the ProjectSteering Committee to provide overall policy guidance & strategic direction for Project Implementation as described in the PIM. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 1. (b) | Description :Establish, prior to initiating implementation and maintainthroughout period of Implementation, a Project Coordination Unit within DAL for M&E of Project with the powers & staff as set inPIM. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 2. (a) | Description :CIC & Cocoa Board to establish & maintain for the period ofProject Implementation, a Technical Appraisal Committee, and within 3 months of Effective Date, train its members as required inPIM. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 2. (b) | Description :Establish, prior to finalization of the first annual work plan,and thereafter, maintain throughout Project Implementation, an Industry Coordination Committee each for cocoa & coffee matters. |Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 3. (a) | Description :Not later than 6 months from Effective Date, carry out baselinesurvey of smallholder households' conditions to measure extent the to which Project objective and outcomes have been achieved. |DueDate :30-Oct-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 3. (b) | Description :Implement an information management system satisfactory to theAssociation. | Due Date :31-Dec-2013

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 3. (c) | Description :Carry out the financial management plan included in the ProjectImplementation Manual in accordance with its terms. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A. 3. (d) | Description :Inform the Association of the progress made in theimplementation of the Environmental and Social Management Framework and Compensation Policy Framework and of any issues that mayarise. | Frequency :Quarterly
